—ЩParchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/math_min.mdЩ@e7858735c763ccb8c8e9f4e5d56b37b1a4b7331877da1c0e39f676fe72b9257bЇtitle: math min‘ЁExamplesЪБCompute the minimum of a list of numbers.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [-50 100 25] | math min
-50

```
Compute the minima of the columns of a table.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [{a: 1 b: 3} {a: 2 b: -1}] | math min
в•­в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”¬в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•®
