в”‚ b в”‚ -1 в”‚
в•°в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”ґв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•Ї

```
Find the minimum of a list of arbitrary values (Warning: Weird).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [-50 'hello' true] | math min
true

```
